name: Self-Leveling Rotary Laser
meta_description: The LMH-C Electronic Self-Leveling rotary Lasers offer fast and simple leveling power to handle your toughest indoor/outdoor jobs with less manpower.
description: The LMH-C Electronic Self-Leveling rotary Lasers offer fast and simple leveling power to handle your toughest indoor/outdoor jobs with less manpower.
short_description:
• Single beam offers 600 RPM rotational for optimal use with detector or depth sensor
  • Anti-Drift system to signal operator when unit is moved out of position Automatic/Manual mode
  • No bubble required - Wide self-leveling range of +/- 5degrees (1 degree per second in horizontal)
summary:
Other Features:

  • Low Battery Indicator so you don't run out of power at the wrong time
  • Heavy duty glass enclosed beacon and durable sealed housing is water and dust-resistant (IPX4) to ensure years of dependable operation
  • Pro Grade - Motorized, electronic horizontal self-leveling

name: Transit-Level
meta_description: For builders that require rough angle turning and fine tuning adjustments
description: For builders that require rough angle turning and fine tuning adjustments
short_description:

name: 8' Aluminum Grade Rod Feet, Tenths, Hundredths, 3 section
meta_title: 8' Aluminum Grade Rod Feet, Tenths, Hundredths, 3 section
small_image_label: 8' Aluminum Grade Rod Feet, Tenths, Hundredths, 3 section
thumbnail_label: 8' Aluminum Grade Rod Feet, Tenths, Hundredths, 3 section
short_description:
• Extends and collapses easily with durable buttons
  • Made of a lightweight and durable aluminum alloy
  • Anodized parts are imprinted with special weather resistant and corrosion resistant inks
  • Sectional junctions are injection molded from a durable, light, impact-resistant plastic
  • Front and back, easy to read scale
  • Scale on back permits easy height readings at eye level
  • Rod Dimensions: 36.8 x 2.6 x 1.8 inches
summary: CST's telescoping aluminum rods are made of a light & durable aluminum alloy.  The anodized  segments are imprinted with exceptional weather resistant and corrosion resistant inks.  Tight tolerances on extruded aluminum parts allow for smooth extension and  deter  unnecessary clattering and slopiness.  The sectional junctions are injection molded from a durable lightweight impact-resistant plastic.  Rods are equipped with  dependable  and wear resistant polycarbonate buttons that  secure  each section.  Easy to read graduations and and a special measuring scale on the rear side allow users to read height at eye level.
meta_keyword: 8' Aluminum Grade Rod Feet, Tenths, Hundredths, 3 section

name: 24X Automatic Level Kit
meta_description: Upgrade to the latest features and technology with CST/berger's SAL Series Automatic Levels!
description: Upgrade to the latest features and technology with CST/berger's SAL Series Automatic Levels!
short_description:
• Magnetically-dampened, wire-hung compensator for optimum range and accuracy
  • Compensator lock protects instrument during transport or storage, also acts as a handy compenstor checking tool
  • Large effective aperture and minimum focus of 1 foot (0.3m)
summary:
• These units now incorporate easy-to-grip styling and an improved compensator.
  • Designed for the contractor, surveyor, or engineer who demands accurate leveling every time, SAL automatic levels set up fast, are easy to use, and save time and money on every job. The SAL Series offers your choice of options: magnification, accuracy, and price.
  • 24X SAL Automatic Level Kit; Includes Tripod and Rod
  • Top-mounted optical peep-sight for quick reference
  • Large, easy-to-use precise focusing knob
  • Easy-to-read horizontal circle
  • Right angle prism for easy bubble viewing
  • Sealed, dust-protected leveling screws
  • Water-resistant, sealed construction plus sunshade for use in various weather conditions
  • Fine motion knobs on left and right sides with friction-braked rotation, endless horizontal drive.
  • 1:100 stadia for distance estimation
  • 5/8-11 threads to fit standard tripods
  • Available in 360 degrees or 400 gons; please specify
  • Includes hardshell carrying case with dual latches, plumb bob, Allen wrench, adjusting pin, and instruction manual.

summary: The AL-500HV is a horizontal and vertical dual-beam single-slope interior and exterior rotary laser that delivers professional performance at an affordable price. The AL-500HV is ideal for exterior and interior general construction and aligning jobs such as grading, concrete forms and pads, site prep and elevation transfer as well as interior jobs such as building, drop ceilings, electrical installation and other alignment jobs. 57-AL500HVI (Interior Package) includes: Remote, Glasses, wall-mount, magnetic target, batteries, case, and user's manual. 57-AL500HVDI (Interior Detector Package) includes: Remote, LD-90 Detector with clamp, glasses, wall-mount, magnetic target, batteries, and case. 57-AL500HVPKG (Complete Package) includes: Remote, LD-90 Detector, LD-90 Detector with clamp, glasses, wall-mount, magnetic target, batteries, contractors' aluminum tripod, 8-Feet leveling rod, and case.
